    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Teorema de la bisectriz]]></title>
    <link href="http://rvf0068.github.io/ejemplos-sage/blog/2014/09/05/bisectriz/"/>
    <updated>2014-09-05T12:48:00-05:00</updated>
    <id>http://rvf0068.github.io/ejemplos-sage/blog/2014/09/05/bisectriz</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="sage"><script type="text/x-sage">
a=10
b=3
c=4

raiz = sqrt(c^2+b^2)
x1 = a*(raiz+b)/(raiz+a)
y1 = c*a/(raiz+a)
P=plot((c/b)*x,0,b)+plot((c/(b-a))*(x-a),b,a)+plot((c/(raiz+b))*x,0,x1,color='red')+point([(x1,y1)],size=50)
P.set_aspect_ratio(1)
P.plot()
</script></div>
]]></content>
